    <article aria-labelledby="overview-heading">
      <h2 id="overview-heading">Overview</h2>
      <p>This page contains organized content using lists and tables, embedded media (image, audio, video), and a complete semantic form that uses only HTML5 validation attributes.</p><section id="features" aria-labelledby="features-heading">
    <h3 id="features-heading">Key Features</h3>
    <ol>
      <li>Semantic structure for accessibility (header, nav, main, section, article, footer).</li>
      <li>Use of lists and a well-scoped table to present tabular data.</li>
      <li>Embedded media elements with descriptive text and captions.</li>
      <li>A complete form using labels, fieldsets, and HTML5 validation attributes.</li>
    </ol>
  </section>

  <section id="media" aria-labelledby="media-heading">
